=\"cname\"><span>鉄が生まれる現場〈製鉄所〉</span></div></a></li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        <p><a href=\"javascript:;\"><span class=\"line\">職種と社員を知る</span></a></p>\n        <div class=\"submenu\">\n          <ul>\n            <li><a href=\"../job/\"><div class=\"image\"><img src=\"../image/common/mmenu-03-01.jpg\" alt=\"職種紹介\"></div><div class=\"cname\"><span>職種紹介</span></div></a></li>\n            <li><a href=\"../job/person-index.html\"><div class=\"image\"><img src=\"../image/common/mmenu-03-02.jpg\" alt=\"社員紹介 ｜ INDEX\"></div><div class=\"cname\"><span>社員紹介 ｜ INDEX</span></div></a></li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        <p><a href=\"javascript:;\"><span class=\"line\">プロジェクトを知る</span></a></p>\n        <div class=\"submenu\">\n          <ul>\n            <li><a href=\"../project/jdscom.html\"><div class=\"image\"><img src=\"../image/common/mmenu-04-01.jpg\" alt=\"異常早期検知システムJ-dscom\"></div><div class=\"cname\"><span>異常早期検知システム</span><br><span>J-dscom&reg;</span></div></a></li>\n            <li><a href=\"../project/mexico.html\"><div class=\"image\"><img src=\"../image/common/mmenu-04-02.jpg\" alt=\"メキシコでの溶融亜鉛めっき鋼板製造設備建設\"></div><div class=\"cname\"><span>メキシコでの溶融亜鉛</span><br><span>めっき鋼板製造設備建設</span></div></a></li>\n            <li><a href=\"../project/7cc.html\"><div class=\"image\"><img src=\"../image/common/mmenu-04-03.jpg\" alt=\"第7スラブ連続鋳造機建設プロジェクト\"></div><div class=\"cname\"><span>第7スラブ連続鋳造機</span><br><span>建設プロジェクト</span></div></a></li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        <p><a href=\"javascript:;\"><span class=\"line\">成長とキャリアを知る</span></a></p>\n        <div class=\"submenu\">\n          <ul>\n            <li><a href=\"../career/training.html\"><div class=\"image\"><img src=\"../image/common/mmenu-05-01.jpg\" alt=\"人材育成・研修制度\"></div><div class=\"cname\"><span>人材育成・研修制度</span></div></a></li>\n            <li><a href=\"../career/talk-01.html\"><div class=\"image\"><im